IMAPAccount main
Host 127.0.0.1
Port 1143
User benedikt.zundel@bzun.de
PassCmd "pass show mail/main"
TLSType none
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore main-remote
Account main

MaildirStore main-local
Path ~/mail/main/
Inbox ~/mail/main/INBOX

Channel main
Far :main-remote:
Near :main-local:
Patterns *
Patterns INBOX*
Expunge Both
CopyArrivalDate yes
Sync All
SyncState *
Create Both



